{"tid":250290,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解仲要揀純學術科?","createTime":"2017-05-20T03:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T17:45:21.000Z","uid":77180,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89547b72c6263053cc2aad663081da989520ab89","tid":250290,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔諗住做research嘅話<br />\n有興趣嘅點解唔以後空餘時間自學<br />\n根本出到黎唔需要用到你呢d知識<br />\n<br />\nP.s唔係反對追求知識，只係見到讀到三大出黎都乞食好心up，讀ive實用科可能仲有用"},{"pid":"d0bcd67760a50c538200a6cbace9c9a97f80b47a","tid":250290,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"除左專業工種外<br />\n呢個世界仲有好多工<br />\n你有信心揾到份非專業荀工如政府工嘅話<br />\n咁咪無必要讀專科"},{"pid":"7b64daa8026aad231e010435e280d0f4de43286b","tid":250290,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左專業工種外<br />\n呢個世界仲有好多工<br />\n你有信心揾到份非專業荀工如政府工嘅話<br />\n咁咪無必要讀專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都啱<br />\n但眼見大把science文社科一車車出黎揸兜好心up<br />\n中學老師可唔可以咪水9人興趣行先<br />\n追求興趣唔一定要讀嗰科<br />\n除非有翻咁上下家底"},{"pid":"3c0665c162ed9b866264acc07be58152c7ccd661","tid":250290,"uid":66379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左專業工種外<br />\n呢個世界仲有好多工<br />\n你有信心揾到份非專業荀工如政府工嘅話<br />\n咁咪無必要讀專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都啱<br />\n但眼見大把science文社科一車車出黎揸兜好心up<br />\n中學老師可唔可以咪水9人興趣行先<br />\n追求興趣唔一定要讀嗰科<br />\n除非有翻咁上下家底</blockquote><br />\nfresh grad人工差四五千 唔等於成世都差過人  都係靠CV interview 姐  加上非專業工既數量一定比專業工既數量多  如果engine仔做唔番engine做 （比人炒） 份CV又唔好 分分鐘仲乞食過垃圾曬銀"},{"pid":"4615616c1bfc4e3542ebe1968c194d49037e80f1","tid":250290,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"冇修理科 除左文史社科 有咩係實用又可以揀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e1d19e927a4bc1e82aa8d60a316dd6a76831a4","tid":250290,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"好多時都係為興趣<br />\n有啲好深入嘅野例如quantum physics、topology之類 自學係非常困難(除非你係世紀天才之類)<br />\n但係偏偏你就係淨係對個啲野有興趣<br />\n咁當然如果你係三餐不繼手停口停都仲去追求興趣<br />\n你就要承受個後果<br />\n<br />\n利伸 讀science"},{"pid":"bb95f14e8ab654789413cf0844af558ba1a6df59","tid":250290,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時都係為興趣<br />\n有啲好深入嘅野例如quantum physics、topology之類 自學係非常困難(除非你係世紀天才之類)<br />\n但係偏偏你就係淨係對個啲野有興趣<br />\n咁當然如果你係三餐不繼手停口停都仲去追求興趣<br />\n你就要承受個後果<br />\n<br />\n利伸 讀science</blockquote><br />\n如果有心讀上去又讀到phd都OK。但係競爭太大，而且做到博士已經30歲，如果搵唔到大學工就大鑊"},{"pid":"574a26bf9062b244a55c940afd3f75dea35aafc6","tid":250290,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"唔夠分揀神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6980768bf1048bd5064782c03054ae9783d12836","tid":250290,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時都係為興趣<br />\n有啲好深入嘅野例如quantum physics、topology之類 自學係非常困難(除非你係世紀天才之類)<br />\n但係偏偏你就係淨係對個啲野有興趣<br />\n咁當然如果你係三餐不繼手停口停都仲去追求興趣<br />\n你就要承受個後果<br />\n<br />\n利伸 讀science</blockquote><br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b533192f1df587b2a3323b1e4cc1f924841b9657","tid":250290,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時都係為興趣<br />\n有啲好深入嘅野例如quantum physics、topology之類 自學係非常困難(除非你係世紀天才之類)<br />\n但係偏偏你就係淨係對個啲野有興趣<br />\n咁當然如果你係三餐不繼手停口停都仲去追求興趣<br />\n你就要承受個後果<br />\n<br />\n利伸 讀science</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好欣賞你呢份勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當年就係無呢份勇氣<br />\n不過都無乜後悔<br />\n始終覺得社會係咁就唯有屈服<br />\n太多first hon grad乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec12e2ff0be2c0a642a84693b7503c58b37ddc6","tid":250290,"uid":75025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"就算讀個科係純學術，但其實滿足自己係知識層面既追求既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都會覺得人生有一大目標達到左，好開心～"},{"pid":"f0fa3100bca52aeda18b0b34e9d603b12a0e0ff6","tid":250290,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"因為唔係個個都追求搵錢<br />\n有朋友明知自己乞食都去讀純文科 一樣生活得好開心<br />\n公屋 真窮 完全無家底"},{"pid":"2f98cc74ec0deea8c2849b6747f62407267ae1e0","tid":250290,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"你估個個都好似你咁窮咩"},{"pid":"fba44e12cd308b34704351970f36f3c705e39556","tid":250290,"uid":20001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左專業工種外<br />\n呢個世界仲有好多工<br />\n你有信心揾到份非專業荀工如政府工嘅話<br />\n咁咪無必要讀專科</blockquote><br />\n中文系冇野撈好彩咁岩入到政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29589e98e06d83dea8fdca1834bc001e9da2b187","tid":250290,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"你根本唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋讀其他科嘅話連畢業都有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申maths grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純數對我嚟講係最容易，workload最細嘅科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c698a57468589882c361bb1850c82b044d4fb8ec","tid":250290,"uid":79635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"唔好將你個學歷同你搵錢能力掛勾<br />\n咁諗會好d"},{"pid":"f3961b729334fedaa0f92046b443438237cf1d28","tid":250290,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你估個個都好似你咁窮咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得喇威喇"},{"pid":"ab6df0e2642fdd9593552e0d93568fd08bf5ed7a","tid":250290,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好將你個學歷同你搵錢能力掛勾<br />\n咁諗會好d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係事實係有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然創業撚就咩科都得"},{"pid":"83d9d7e6224e6b1c000f11713cd4938da9273afa","tid":250290,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多時都係為興趣<br />\n有啲好深入嘅野例如quantum physics、topology之類 自學係非常困難(除非你係世紀天才之類)<br />\n但係偏偏你就係淨係對個啲野有興趣<br />\n咁當然如果你係三餐不繼手停口停都仲去追求興趣<br />\n你就要承受個後果<br />\n<br />\n利伸 讀science</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好欣賞你呢份勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當年就係無呢份勇氣<br />\n不過都無乜後悔<br />\n始終覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">社會係咁就唯有屈服</span><br />\n太多first hon grad乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔認命囉<br />\n同埋覺得庸庸碌碌過一世<br />\n由得自己變做一個安穩既社會上班族<br />\n同精神上死左無乜分別<br />\n<br />\n與其係咁不如盡地一搏<br />\n就算失敗都好，都起碼精彩過呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我當時的確係咁諗既...</span>"},{"pid":"1644e3b2a4bb01f0771043260ecc75f25dd7277a","tid":250290,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"為興趣<br />\n屋企無經濟壓力<br />\n多數呢兩類"},{"pid":"8374d5c6df5067d5f95584e400447b029190eb6e","tid":250290,"uid":25029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"讀完一年電腦發現興趣係好緊要 個一年所有professor都話電腦好有前途 fg二萬唔出奇 但真係頂唔順 黎緊去讀連高登所謂既乞食科 仲要2個major打孖上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e27205605475078c01f7579dbff306cacddc79","tid":250290,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完一年電腦發現興趣係好緊要 個一年所有professor都話電腦好有前途 fg二萬唔出奇 但真係頂唔順 黎緊